{"tid":2326493,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警方搗破跨境賣淫集團　兩周接觸逾二千名嫖客","createTime":"2020-12-15T11:01:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-15T11:49:18.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"797ec8013fc9ab007736aa5f6e0d3afc67535669","tid":2326493,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T11:01:22.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】警方瓦解一個跨境賣淫集團，拘捕31人，相信過去兩星期接觸過二、三千名嫖客。<br />\n<br />\n警方行動中，檢獲41萬現金等證物，探員星期日搜查酒店及無牌按摩院等，拘捕31人包括4名集團主腦及27名非法入境者，相信集團透過通訊軟件，在內地招攬成員來港賣淫，為她們提供酒店住宿。每一至兩星期轉換賣淫場所，又在酒店大堂安排人手把風，增加調查難度。警方提醒市民在疫情期間，減少跟陌生人有親密接觸。<br />\n<br />\n油尖警區行動主任甄瀚揚：「即使沒有被警察拘捕，她都不會通知你，而你都可以想像到這些嫖客不會四處告訴人，接觸過這些人，正正因為這樣，希望大家在疫情這樣的情況盡本份，不要作出自私的行為。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=416715\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D416715&d=ZAqn3h4t0e4XfOyVRCtvGJ2AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=aef4290a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D416715&h=2721e71c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=416715</a>"},{"pid":"9cdc3a1b5df78e75e992c50a7e5bad0811684d9e","tid":2326493,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T11:02:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"649b2a3837c84fa198d7a3dad77baaa41684d47f","tid":2326493,"uid":17641,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T11:03:26.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>二千名黑警享受完後就封艇拉人</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cce0f80f43ad344573d5aec7a1b760e44552d67e","tid":2326493,"uid":308264,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T11:04:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"364ae4ea6